{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-45-triangular-pentagonal-and-hexagonal","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-1-to-100","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 45: Brojevi za pentagon, pentagonalni i heksagonalni","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Brojevi za trokutasti, pentagonala i heksagonalni oblici generišu se korišćenjem sledećih formula:</p>\n<div style='display: inline-grid; text-align: center; grid-template-columns: 135px 135px 260px; grid-template-rows: auto;'><div>Pembetatu</div><div>T<sub>n</sub>=<var>n</var>(<var>n</var>+1)/2</div><div>1, 3, 6, 10, 15, ...</div></div>\n<div style='display: inline-grid; text-align: center; grid-template-columns: 135px 135px 260px; grid-template-rows: auto;'><div>Pentagonalno</div><div>P<sub>n</sub>=<var>n</var>(3<var>n</var>−1)/2</div><div>1, 5, 12, 22, 35, ...</div></div>\n<div style='display: inline-grid; text-align: center; grid-template-columns: 135px 135px 260px; grid-template-rows: auto;'><div>Heksagonalno</div><div>H<sub>n</sub>=<var>n</var>(2<var>n</var>−1)</div><div>1, 6, 15, 28, 45, ...</div></div>\n<p>Može se potvrditi da T<sub>285</sub> = P<sub>165</sub> = H<sub>143</sub> = 40755.</p>\n<p>Pronađi sljedeći broj koji je trougaoni, a istovremeno i pentagonalan i heksagonalan.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f3991000cf542c50feac","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302122,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-45-triangular-pentagonal-and-hexagonal"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function triPentaHexa(n) {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\ntriPentaHexa(40756);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>triPentaHexa(40756)</code> trebalo bi da vrati broj.</p>","testString":"assert(typeof triPentaHexa(40756) === 'number');"},{"text":"<p><code>triPentaHexa(40756)</code> trebalo bi da vrati 1533776805.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(triPentaHexa(40756), 1533776805);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-1-to-100","dashedName":"problem-45-triangular-pentagonal-and-hexagonal","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-1-to-100","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-46-goldbachs-other-conjecture","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-44-pentagon-numbers","id":"5900f3991000cf542c50feac","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function arrangedProbability(limit) {\n  // Based on https://www.mathblog.dk/project-euler-100-blue-discs-two-blue/\n  let blue = 15;\n  let discs = 21;\n\n  while (discs < limit) {\n    const nextBlue = 3 * blue + 2 * discs - 2;\n    const nextDiscs = 4 * blue + 3 * discs - 3;\n\n    blue = nextBlue;\n    discs = nextDiscs;\n  }\n  return blue;\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-1-to-100/problem-45-triangular-pentagonal-and-hexagonal"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}